All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<Node>, Element, Graph, AttributeSink, ElementSink, Pipe, Sink, Source
public class MultiGraph
extends DefaultGraph

A graph implementation that supports multiple edges between two nodes.

This implementation is only a subclass of DefaultGraph that renames it and add no behaviour excepted changing the node and edge factories to use the MultiNode and MultiEdge classes.
